Celtic lost 3-2 to Inverness in the Scottish Cup semi-final on Sunday . 
  The Hoops have written to the Scottish Football Association to gain an 'understanding' of the refereeing decisions during the game . 
  Celtic striker Leigh Griffiths had a goal-bound shot blocked by Josh Meekings in the first-half . 
  Caley Thistle went on to win the game after extra-time . 
  Celtic were denied a domestic Treble after the defeat . 
 